ZH: 我买了几个新的衣架，可以挂更多的衣服。
EN: I bought a few new hangers so I can hang more clothes.

ZH: 她在衣架上挂了一件漂亮的连衣裙。
EN: She hung a beautiful dress on the hanger.

ZH: 我的衣橱里的衣架太拥挤了，我需要清理一下。
EN: The hangers in my closet are too crowded, I need to clean it up.

ZH: 每次洗衣服之后，都要把衣架放回原位。
EN: After washing clothes each time, I always put the hangers back in place.

ZH: 我的皮夹衣架上挂着我的大衣。
EN: My leather jacket is hanging on the coat hanger.

ZH: 请把这件衬衫放在衣架上晾干。
EN: Please hang this shirt on the hanger to dry.

ZH: 衣架上挂着我的新衣服，我可以穿去别的地方。
EN: My new clothes are hanging on the hanger, I can wear them somewhere else.

ZH: 这个衣架可以收缩，方便携带。
EN: This hanger can be folded, making it easy to carry.

ZH: 请确保每个人都有足够的衣架挂衣服。
EN: Make sure everyone has enough hangers to hang their clothes.

ZH: 衣架上挂着几条领带，看起来整齐又方便取用。
EN: There are a few ties hanging on the tie hanger, looking neat and easy to access.

ZH: 我在家里有一个专门挂围巾的衣架。
EN: I have a special hanger at home for hanging scarves.

ZH: 我的衣柜上都是上铺衣架，下铺可以挂鞋。
EN: The top of my wardrobe is all hangers, and the bottom is for hanging shoes.

ZH: 他喜欢用木头衣架，觉得更有质感。
EN: He likes to use wooden hangers, he thinks they have a better texture.

ZH: 衣架上的毛衣被放得太挤，容易变形。
EN: The sweater on the hanger is too crowded, it is easy to deform.

ZH: 请把所有的衣架都清理干净，以备下一次使用。
EN: Please clean all the hangers for the next use.

ZH: 我的衣柜里没有多余的衣架了，我需要再去买一些。
EN: There are no extra hangers in my wardrobe, I need to buy some more.

ZH: 这家店里的衣架种类繁多，你可以挑选自己喜欢的。
EN: The shop has a wide variety of hangers, you can choose the ones you like.

ZH: 衣架上悬挂着时尚的配饰，为房间增色不少。
EN: The hangers are adorned with stylish accessories, adding color to the room.

ZH: 这个细节设计的衣架很有质感，适合搭配高档衣物。
